%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^ORANGE%^Chaos Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

This domains grants its users the ability to cause chaos and revel in all things anarchic.

Clerics with the Chaos Domain gain the following benefits:
- %^CYAN%^BOLD%^enhance%^RESET%^ command to place the anarchic enhancement on your weapon.
- %^ORANGE%^Touch of Chaos%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The chaos domain contains the following spells:

Hideous Laughter, Chaos Hammer, Confusion, Spellscar, Irresistable Dance

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nilith, Khyron

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
